The Babysitter;;1995;;R;;Drama,Thriller;;4.3;;Guy Ferland;;Alicia Silverstone,Jeremy London,J.T. Walsh,Lee Garlington,Nicky Katt,Lois Chiles,George Segal,Ryan Slater,Brittany English Stephens,Tuesday Knight,Eric Menyuk,Matthew Kimbrough,Jane Alden,Noel Evangelisti,Michael Chieffo,Hal Fort Atkinson III,Monty Silverstone,Cameron Fuller;;A teenage girl babysits two young kids while the parents go out to a party. Her boyfriend is coerced (with the help of alcohol) by an old 'friend' into going to the house. Both boys are obsessed with the babysitter, as is the father of the two children. The story basically shows the effects drink has on different people.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0112438/